13	//! - Determinism on (seed, sigma) and the 6-sigma bound on Gaussian
14	//!   deltas.
15	//! - The source model is never affected by a perturb on its clone.
16	//! - Error handling for unknown families, wrong arity, non-model
17	//!   arguments.
